# 🧠 TextMorph  
### AI-Powered Content Simplification, Summarization & Paraphrasing

---

## 🧩 Milestone 4 – Final Integration

TextMorph is a complete end-to-end AI-powered application that transforms complex text into clear, concise, and understandable content using advanced NLP models.

---

## 📌 Overview

Milestone 4 focuses on integrating all previously developed modules into a fully functional application.

This includes:

- 🔐 User Authentication (Milestone 1)  
- 📝 Text Processing (Milestone 2)  
- 🤖 AI Model Integration (Milestone 3)  

The final system is deployed using **Streamlit** and exposed via **Ngrok**.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Integrate authentication, NLP processing, and AI models  
- Build a complete end-to-end application  
- Provide a user-friendly interface  
- Enable real-time text transformation  

---

## 🚀 Features Implemented

### 👤 User Features

- Secure login/signup (JWT-based authentication)  
- Input text for processing  
- Text Summarization (Short / Medium / Long)  
- Paraphrasing (Simple / Neutral / Advanced)  
- Readability Analysis  
- Side-by-side comparison (Input vs Output)  
- Save history of operations  
- Feedback system  

---

### 🛠 Admin Features

- View all users  
- Manage user roles  
- Monitor application usage  
- View feedback and ratings  
- Access complete history logs  
- Feedback analytics (WordCloud)  

---

## 🧩 System Architecture

| Component        | Technology Used              |
|----------------|-----------------------------|
| Frontend        | Streamlit                   |
| Backend         | Python                      |
| NLP Processing  | NLTK                        |
| AI Models       | Hugging Face Transformers   |
| Database        | SQLite / MySQL              |
| Security        | JWT Authentication          |

---

